dzen2-based conky by fog.

Dependencies:
conky, dzen2, curl, aptitude

Copy  dzicons folder and conkyrc_dzen_mine inside .conky folder.
Rename scripts folder .scripts and copy it inside your home.
Change paths, country code, dimensions for your screen and username/password (NOT SECURE they are in plain text format) for your needs. 
Make dzenbar.sh executable, put it somewhere in yout path and add it in autostart.

Enjoy.


